                    ipsa que.</span
                  >
                </div></a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2 max-w-md"
                ><Image
                  src={ImgLandingPage}
                  alt="ImgLandingPage"
                  class="w-20"
                /><div class="flex flex-col">
                  <h3 class="text-base font-bold font-poppins">
                    Desarrollo de Landing Pages
                  </h3><span class="text-xs/4"
                    >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit.
                    Iusto, eaque distinctio! Cupiditate atque exercitationem
                    ipsa que.</span
                  >
                </div></a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2 max-w-md"
                ><Image
                  src={ImgEcommerce}
                  alt="ImgEcommerce"
                  class="w-20"
                /><div class="flex flex-col">
                  <h3 class="text-base font-bold font-poppins">
                    Desarrollo de Tiendas Virtuales
                  </h3><span class="text-xs/4"
                    >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit.
                    Iusto, eaque distinctio! Cupiditate atque exercitationem
